<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Actions ===
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Under a user's profile, there are several actions that you can take, these will vary depending on whether you have the user added as a friend or not.
</div>

[[File:UserProfile_UserActions.webp|thumb|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Actions available for a non-friended user.</span>]]
[[File:UserProfile_FriendActions.webp|thumb|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Actions available for a friended user.</span>]]


{| class="wikitable"
!<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Action</span>
!<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Description</span>
