|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Join<ref group="actions" name="friends-only">These actions can only be performed on friends.</ref></span>
|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Joins the user's instance.</span>
|-
|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Request Invite<ref group="actions" name="friends-only"></ref></span>
|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Sends the user a notification informing them that you would like to join their instance. The notification includes a customizable message and with [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]] a photo can also be added to the notification.</span>
|-
