|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Sends the user an invitation to join your instance. The invite includes a customizable message and with [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+|VRC+]] a photo can also be added to the invitation.</span>
|-
|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Gift VRC+</span>
